OL,3,CThree men arrested after teenager
OL,4,Ccritically injured in Bradford hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FThey turned around to pursue the car
OL,8,Fbut lost sight of it.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "Officers then
OL,11,Flocated a pedestrian on Halifax Road
OL,12,Fwho had been hit by the suspect
OL,13,Fvehicle which had failed to stop at
OL,14,Fthe scene."
OL,16,FTwo 33-year-old men were arrested on
OL,17,FTuesday, 17 September, one on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving and leaving the
OL,20,Fscene. The other was arrested on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
