OL,7,FA third man, aged 24, was arrested on
OL,8,FWednesday, 18 September on suspicion
OL,9,Fof causing serious injury by dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FAll three men remain in police custody.
OL,14,FThe road remained closed on Tuesday
OL,15,Fmorning but has since reopened.
OL,17,FThe force has referred itself to the
OL,18,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct.
